iCBT iPRT 89 (52) 90 (63) Yes Australia Compared iCBT to Internet-based progressive
relaxation training (iPRT) for OCD. While both
interventions showed promise, iCBT led to significant
improvement in OCD severity. Challenges included
participant engagement for post-treatment
assessments and deviations from the protocol.
