18–65 65.9 Diag. CAT Woebot Waiting list 88 (71) 92 (81) No USA Evaluated Woebot-SUDs (W-SUDs), a digital health
solution, in reducing substance misuse during COVID-19.
In an 8-week RCT, W-SUDs users showed significant
reductions in substance use and improved mental health
outcomes. Limitations included a small sample size and
self-reported data, but findings suggest W-SUDs may
mitigate barriers to traditional treatment.
